parameters: Kru: "Umi... I'm so glad you're safe..."

Kru: "That's right... But... I was able to rescue you, and that's what Mia
always wanted..."
Kru: "Ah... It seems it's time to say goodbye..."

Kru: "Because I came from the future... I'm being sent back to my original
time..."

Kru: "It's okay... The Kru from this time will stay, so Umi can be happy
with that Kru..."
Kru: "It's okay... Everything will be alright... It will all work out..."
